 *  any actions, just build the tree.
 *
 *  The phases are:
 *
 *		A3Lexer.g (this file)
 *              A3Parser.g
 *              A3Verify.g (derived from A3Walker.g)
 *		assign.types.g
 *		define.g
 *		buildnfa.g
 *		antlr.print.g (optional)
 *		codegen.g
 *
 *  Terence Parr
 *  University of San Francisco
 *  2005
 *  Jim Idle (this v3 grammar)
 *  Temporal Wave LLC
 *  2009
